<p>GDP growth: 6.3%  GDP: $68bn (PPP: $126bn) Inflation: 7.1% Population: 20.8m GDP per head: $3,260 (PPP: $6,040)</p>

<p>The popular president, Mahinda Rajapakse, and his United People's Freedom Alliance will continue to reap the dividend of victory over Tamil separatists in 2009. The  priority will be to rebuild infrastructure destroyed or neglected in the war and to spur rural development. Tensions arising from Mr Rajapakse's personalised, hardline approach will build ominously, but this should be a year of consolidation and growth. </p>

